-- Louisiana Gov asks government to tap oil stockpile
-- 
-- Mon Sep 1, 2008 1:58pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/01/us-storm-gustav-energy-spr-idUSN0131608220080901

 

 HOUSTON  (Reuters) - Louisiana Gov. Bobby Jindal on Monday called on the federal government to release emergency crude oil supplies to counteract fuel shortages due to Hurricane Gustav. 

 (Reporting by  Chris Baltimore )